snippet.title: Total War: Warhammer 2: The Battle of the Fallen Gates - The PC Gaming Show 2017
snippet.description:
The Total War: Warhammer 2 cinematic from the PC Gaming Show. It's the High Elves vs. the LIzardmen! Warhammer 2 is out September 28th, 2017.

Watch the PC Gaming Show: http://www.pcgamer.com/watch-pc-gaming-show-2017-e3-livestream/
